<heading id="D0EE81FAFFEE3A09FF5BA033FDF6F9DF" centered="true" fontSize="8" level="2" pageId="3" pageNumber="387" reason="8">
MONOPHYLY OF 
<taxonomicName id="4C194D15FFEE3A09FE05A033FD58F9BC" authorityName="Lopez and Castello" authorityYear="1966" box="[396,692,1566,1587]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Sternopygidae" genus="Eigenmannia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Gymnotiformes" pageId="3" pageNumber="414" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="trilineata">
<emphasis id="B96DEA84FFEE3A09FE05A033FD58F9BC" box="[396,692,1566,1587]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="387">EIGENMANNIA TRILINEATA</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
SPECIES- GROUP
</heading>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C303651DFFEE3A09FF19A049FBB2F9A2" pageId="3" pageNumber="387" type="materials_examined">
<paragraph id="8BA63696FFEE3A09FF19A049FBB2F9A2" blockId="3.[144,759,1636,1902]" lastBlockId="3.[806,1422,1287,1584]" pageId="3" pageNumber="387">
All genera of the 
<taxonomicName id="4C194D15FFEE3A09FEDEA049FE16F9F7" authorityName="Cope" authorityYear="1871" box="[343,506,1636,1658]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Sternopygidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Gymnotiformes" pageId="3" pageNumber="387" phylum="Chordata" rank="family">Sternopygidae</taxonomicName>
(see comparative material examined) were used for the purpose of character polarization. The results revealed a putative synapomorphy that supports the monophyly of the 
<taxonomicName id="4C194D15FFEE3A09FF45A0F2FE8BF97E" authorityName="Lopez and Castello" authorityYear="1966" box="[204,359,1758,1780]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Sternopygidae" genus="Eigenmannia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Gymnotiformes" pageId="3" pageNumber="387" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="trilineata">
<emphasis id="B96DEA84FFEE3A09FF45A0F2FE8BF97E" box="[204,359,1758,1780]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="387">E. trilineata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
species group (
<taxonomicName id="4C194D15FFEE3A09FDC6A0F2FF1DF89E" authority="Peixoto &amp; Dutra &amp; Wosiacki, 2015" authorityName="Peixoto &amp; Dutra &amp; Wosiacki" authorityYear="2015" class="Actinopterygii" family="Sternopygidae" genus="Eigenmannia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Gymnotiformes" pageId="3" pageNumber="387" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="antonioi" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis id="B96DEA84FFEE3A09FDC6A0F2FF1DF89E" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="387">Eigenmannia antonioi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="A25E57FFFFEE3A09FF71A0D0FEBFF89F" box="[248,339,1789,1810]" pageId="3" pageNumber="387" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
, 
<taxonomicName id="4C194D15FFEE3A09FEEAA0D3FD7CF89F" authority="Peixoto &amp; Dutra &amp; Wosiacki, 2015" authorityName="Peixoto &amp; Dutra &amp; Wosiacki" authorityYear="2015" box="[355,656,1789,1811]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Sternopygidae" genus="Eigenmannia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Gymnotiformes" pageId="3" pageNumber="387" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="desantanai" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis id="B96DEA84FFEE3A09FEEAA0D3FD7CF89F" box="[355,656,1789,1811]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="387">Eigenmannia desantanai</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="A25E57FFFFEE3A09FD11A0D0FD1EF89F" box="[664,754,1789,1810]" pageId="3" pageNumber="387" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
, 
<taxonomicName id="4C194D15FFEE3A09FF19A131FE2FF8BC" authority="Peixoto &amp; Dutra &amp; Wosiacki, 2015" authorityName="Peixoto &amp; Dutra &amp; Wosiacki" authorityYear="2015" box="[144,451,1820,1841]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Sternopygidae" genus="Eigenmannia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Gymnotiformes" pageId="3" pageNumber="387" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="guairaca" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis id="B96DEA84FFEE3A09FF19A131FE2FF8BC" box="[144,451,1820,1841]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="387">Eigenmannia guairaca</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="A25E57FFFFEE3A09FE45A131FDC2F8BC" box="[460,558,1820,1841]" pageId="3" pageNumber="387" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
, 
<taxonomicName id="4C194D15FFEE3A09FDC7A131FED7F8DD" authority="Peixoto &amp; Dutra &amp; Wosiacki, 2015" authorityName="Peixoto &amp; Dutra &amp; Wosiacki" authorityYear="2015" class="Actinopterygii" family="Sternopygidae" genus="Eigenmannia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Gymnotiformes" pageId="3" pageNumber="387" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="matintapereira" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis id="B96DEA84FFEE3A09FDC7A131FED7F8DD" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="387">Eigenmannia matintapereira</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="A25E57FFFFEE3A09FEC8A116FE74F8DD" box="[321,408,1851,1872]" pageId="3" pageNumber="387" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
, 
<taxonomicName id="4C194D15FFEE3A09FE2EA116FDA7F8DD" baseAuthorityName="Reinhardt" baseAuthorityYear="1852" box="[423,587,1851,1872]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Sternopygidae" genus="Eigenmannia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Gymnotiformes" pageId="3" pageNumber="387" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="microstoma">
<emphasis id="B96DEA84FFEE3A09FE2EA116FDA7F8DD" box="[423,587,1851,1872]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="387">E. microstoma</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="4C194D15FFEE3A09FDD4A116FECFF8E3" authority="Peixoto &amp; Dutra &amp; Wosiacki, 2015" authorityName="Peixoto &amp; Dutra &amp; Wosiacki" authorityYear="2015" class="Actinopterygii" family="Sternopygidae" genus="Eigenmannia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Gymnotiformes" pageId="3" pageNumber="387" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="muirapinima" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis id="B96DEA84FFEE3A09FDD4A116FECFF8E3" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="387">Eigenmannia muirapinima</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="A25E57FFFFEE3A09FEA1A174FE97F8E3" box="[296,379,1881,1902]" pageId="3" pageNumber="387" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
, 
<taxonomicName id="4C194D15FFEE3A09FE0FA174FD76F8E3" authority="Peixoto &amp; Dutra &amp; Wosiacki, 2015" authorityName="Peixoto &amp; Dutra &amp; Wosiacki" authorityYear="2015" box="[390,666,1881,1902]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Sternopygidae" genus="Eigenmannia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Gymnotiformes" pageId="3" pageNumber="387" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="pavulagem" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis id="B96DEA84FFEE3A09FE0FA174FD76F8E3" box="[390,666,1881,1902]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="387">Eigenmannia pavulagem</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="A25E57FFFFEE3A09FD29A174FD1FF8E3" box="[672,755,1881,1902]" pageId="3" pageNumber="387" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
, 
<taxonomicName id="4C194D15FFEE3A09FCAFA32AFC56FA91" authorityName="Lopez and Castello" authorityYear="1966" box="[806,954,1287,1308]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Sternopygidae" genus="Eigenmannia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Gymnotiformes" pageId="3" pageNumber="387" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="trilineata">
<emphasis id="B96DEA84FFEE3A09FCAFA32AFC56FA91" box="[806,954,1287,1308]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="387">E. trilineata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="4C194D15FFEE3A09FC46A32AFB71FA91" authorityName="Triques" authorityYear="1996" box="[975,1181,1287,1308]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Sternopygidae" genus="Eigenmannia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Gymnotiformes" pageId="3" pageNumber="387" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="vicentespelaea">
<emphasis id="B96DEA84FFEE3A09FC46A32AFB71FA91" box="[975,1181,1287,1308]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="387">E. vicentespelaea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, and 
<taxonomicName id="4C194D15FFEE3A09FB62A32AFC95FAB6" authority="Peixoto &amp; Dutra &amp; Wosiacki, 2015" authorityName="Peixoto &amp; Dutra &amp; Wosiacki" authorityYear="2015" class="Actinopterygii" family="Sternopygidae" genus="Eigenmannia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Gymnotiformes" pageId="3" pageNumber="387" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="waiwai" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis id="B96DEA84FFEE3A09FB62A32AFC95FAB6" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="387">Eigenmannia waiwai</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="A25E57FFFFEE3A09FC09A30BFC34FAB6" box="[896,984,1318,1339]" pageId="3" pageNumber="387" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
): presence of a superior medial stripe. The species of the Eigenmanniinae lack a stripe characterized by a concentration of chromatophores between the lateral line and the proximal portion of the pterygiophores of the anal fin. In contrast, this character is uniquely present in all species of the 
<taxonomicName id="4C194D15FFEE3A09FA85A392FA61FA5E" authorityName="Lopez and Castello" authorityYear="1966" box="[1292,1421,1470,1492]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Sternopygidae" genus="Eigenmannia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Gymnotiformes" pageId="3" pageNumber="387" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="trilineata">
<emphasis id="B96DEA84FFEE3A09FA85A392FA61FA5E" box="[1292,1421,1470,1492]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="387">E. trilineata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
species group. This feature is consequently hypothesized to be an exclusive synapomorphy for the 
<taxonomicName id="4C194D15FFEE3A09FCAFA036FC5DF9A2" authorityName="Lopez and Castello" authorityYear="1966" box="[806,945,1562,1584]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Sternopygidae" genus="Eigenmannia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Gymnotiformes" pageId="3" pageNumber="387" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="trilineata">
<emphasis id="B96DEA84FFEE3A09FCAFA036FC5DF9A2" box="[806,945,1562,1584]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="387">E. trilineata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
species group.
</paragraph>
